for full files, selects comments as well    : #.+>|\/\/.+\n|(?s)\/\*.*?\*\/|->|>>=?|<<=?|\|\||&&|[|\^&%<>!\\-+*\/=]?=|--|\+\+|".+"|[\w]+|[\W]|.+
for lines, parses correctly so far          : #.+>|->|>>=?|<<=?|\|\||&&|[|^&%<>!\-+*/=]?=|--|\+\+|".+"|[\w]+|[\W]|.+
no preprocess commands                      : ->|>>=?|<<=?|\|\||&&|[|^&%<>!\-+*/=]?=|--|\+\+|".+"|[\w]+|[\W]|.+
grab include file                           : [\w]+\.h
also grab include file                      : <(.+)>
remove spaces                               : //.+\n|(?s)/\*.*?\*/